    "body": "Pending small items to wrap this up @0xKiwi \r\n- [x] Rename accounts-v2 new to create for consistency \r\n- [x] No mnemonics for direct, we should only show the hex private withdrawal key to stdout\r\n- [x] Remove the `CanUnlockAccounts` property from a wallet. This was old before we had a nice way of differentiating the `NewWallet`  for the different keymanager kinds **IVAN**\r\n- [x] Implement `list` for remote keymanager (it should likely just fetch the validating public keys, assign unique petnames for them using shared/petnames\r\n- [x] Abstract the generateDepositTransaction and logDepositTransaction functions in derived.go and direct.go into some common file, perhaps somewhere in shared/ **IVAN**\r\n- [x] Reduce all the different ways of saving and reading to and from disk in wallet.go into something more general\r\n- [x] Remove `wallet.AccountNames()` in wallet.go as it is only used by direct and should live in direct.go instead\r\n- [x] Rename the list.go, new.go, import.go, export.go files to have the prefix accounts\r\n- [x] Add nicer godoc to the accounts/v2/doc.go file\r\n- [x] Comprehensively test every command to see if it works for the different keymanagers\r\n- [x] Comprehensively go through the usage flags and try --help on every command to see if all the flags make sense (I think wallet create uses PasswordFileFlag for the wallet password but the usage says it the flag is for account passwords)\r\n- [x]  Ensure runtime works for direct keymanager (in progress, deposit sent)\r\n- [x]  Ensure runtime works for derived keymanager (in progress, deposit sent)\r\n- [x]  Ensure runtime works for remote keymanager (needs a remote signer setup, in progress, deposit sent)\r\n- [x] Ensure we use filepath.Join and try everything on windows\r\n- [x] Ensure end-user viewable errors don't display stack traces **IVAN**\r\n- [x] Sanitize passwords from file inputs by trimming end newline chars **IVAN**\r\n- [x] Ensure export/import only works for direct keymanager\r\n- [ ] Comprehensive tests for wallet create\r\n- [x] BLS flags for altona",
